{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7d941c87-653f-4c00-b069-d212ed59454a","content":"Here's what you need to change:\n\n**1. Update package references in your `.csproj`:**\n\n```xml\n<!-- Remove these -->\n<PackageReference Include=\"NUnit3TestAdapter\" Version=\"4.6.0\" />\n<PackageReference Include=\"Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk\" Version=\"...\" />\n\n<!-- Add this -->\n<PackageReference Include=\"NUnit.Runner\" Version=\"4.3.0\" />\n```\n\n**2. Add these properties to your `.csproj`:**\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n  <EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n**3. Run tests with:**\n\n```bash\ndotnet test\n# or run the test executable directly\ndotnet run\n```\n\nThe `NUnit.Runner` package provides the Microsoft.Testing.Platform adapter and auto-generates the entry point. Your existing `[Test]` attributes and test code remain unchanged.\n\nIf you need VSTest compatibility during migration, you can add `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` to keep `dotnet test` working via the bridge.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"a9802193-7b64-4419-a237-3031305156b9","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating their NUnit test project from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform. This is a knowledge question about .NET testing infrastructure migration. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nKey changes needed to migrate NUnit from VSTest (NUnit3TestAdapter) to Microsoft.Testing.Platform:\n\n1. Replace `NUnit3TestAdapter` with `NUnit.Runner` (the Microsoft.Testing.Platform runner for NUnit)\n2. Remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` \n3. Add the appropriate runner package\n4. Update the project file with `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` or similar properties\n\n\n5. Change the output type to executable and enable the testing platform entry point generation so the test project can run as a standalone application\n\n.","outputTokens":732,"requestId":"E82A:11815A:268BDBB:2903A72:6A0493A6"},"id":"b22bf889-a155-4e76-9994-3bbad0c1bff4","timestamp":"2026-05-13T15:07:33.789Z","parentId":"ae3f4d5d-4ace-47e8-ae2e-75d76f750dd0"}
